explanation: [0-0] On a sandy riverbank, a man in swim trunks is preparing for a challenge. He holds a blue tripod connected to a rope, has short brown hair, wears black and light blue swim trunks, is barefoot, and has a black necklace around his neck. Another man in a white T-shirt and khaki shorts is feeding him a drink. A woman with long blonde hair wearing a black bikini is filming with her phone. Two other men are watching in the background. The surrounding vegetation is green, and the sky is grayish-blue.
[0-6] After a few sips, the man who was feeding him walks away, and the woman steps back. The man about to challenge looks up and smiles at the camera.
